snippet.title: ZOMBIE ARENA SURVIVAL - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Kill as many zombies as you can before they kill you.
ZOMBIE ARENA SURVIVAL is a top down shooter where you fight zombies either in melee or ranged combat and try to survive as long as possible before they kill you.

Originally just a prototype for a combat system, Gfeller Entertainment decided to make a little game out of it, which the dev hopes will give a few people some fun.

Developed by Gfeller Entertainment
